    </div>
    <div class="w3-row w3-padding-64" id="menu">
      <div class="w3-col l6 w3-padding-large">
        <h1 class="w3-center">Outcomes</h1><br>
        <p class="w3-text-grey">Implementing these solutions would result in several positive outcomes, including:</p>
        <h4>Enhanced Campus Aesthetics:</h4>
        <p class="w3-text-grey">A significant reduction in water usage will lead to fewer broken or leaking pipes. This will contribute to the overall beauty and appearance of the campus.</p><br>
      
        <h4>Sustainable Environment:</h4>
        <p class="w3-text-grey"> Reducing water waste in LPU campus will help conserve natural resources. Additionally, reducing water usage will indirectly reduce the carbon footprint of the institution.</p><br>
      
        <h4>Economic Savings:</h4>
        <p class="w3-text-grey">The savings realized from reduced water bills can be used for various campus improvements, including new facilities and equipment.</p><br>
      
        <h4>Reduced Waste Disposal:</h4>
        <p class="w3-text-grey">With reduced water usage, there will be less water-related waste to dispose of. This can contribute to the overall reduction of waste on campus.</p><br>
      
        <h4>Stronger Environmental Management:</h4>
        <p class="w3-text-grey"> Adopting a proactive approach to address water wastage in LPU campus will demonstrate the institution's commitment to sustainable practices and responsible environmental management.</p>    
        </div>
